For those of you who don't know how to help with seeding, while the file is downloading in Bittorent you can go to Options>Preferences>Bandwith and set the Maximum Upload Limit to 0 which makes it unlimited. This INCREASES your download speed, since that's how P2P works, the more of the file you share with other people the more they share with you. If only 1 person is seeding it'll take 1 year for you to download this, which it currently will once you get halfway through downloading the file the download speed drops to 2kbs. If no one with the complete file seeds, no one else can download the complete file, so will some of you 147 leechers PLEASE seed.
